details.name: Assassinate
details.description: Sniper locks onto a target enemy unit and, after a short aiming duration, fires a devastating shot that deals damage at long range and mini-stuns the target.
details.upgrade_description: Turns Assassinate into a ground target AoE ability, that, after the aiming duration, launches a critical strike and procs headshot on units in the AoE. Only affects visible heroes.
